  alt="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/ae/Sofocle%2C_copia_romana_da_originale_greco_con_testa_non_pertinente%2C_inv._2242.JPG"></p>
  </td>
  <td width=186 valign=top style='width:139.75pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'>
  <p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><img border=0
  width=139 height=384 id="Picture 14" src="infinitecanonsprint_image015.jpg"></p>
  </td>
  <td width=239 style='width:179.25pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'>
  <p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><img border=0
