  alt="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/ff/Orson_Welles_1937.jpg"></p>
  </td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
  <td width=213 valign=top style='width:159.8pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'>
  <p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'>Sophocles (<i>Oedipus
