  10.0pt'>Roman copy of Greek original. Courtesy Wikimedia Commons.</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width=186 valign=top style='width:139.75pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'>
  <p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'>Tolstoy <span
