  </span><span style='font-size:10.0pt'>“Lev Nikolayevich Tolstoy shoeless,”
  1901, by Repin. Courtesy Wikimedia Commons.</span></p>
  </td>
  <td width=239 valign=top style='width:179.25pt;padding:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt'>
  <p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><span
