style='font-size:13.0pt;font-family:"Garamond","serif"'>[3]</span></span></span></a>
Richard Tobin, “The Canon of Polykleitos,” <i>American Journal of Archaeology</i>
79.4 (Oct., 1975): 307-321.</p>

