</div>

<div id=ftn10>

<p class=MsoFootnoteText><a href="#_ftnref10" name="_ftn10" title=""><span
class=MsoFootnoteReference><span class=MsoFootnoteReference><span
style='font-size:13.0pt;font-family:"Garamond","serif"'>[10]</span></span></span></a>
Commentary on Matthew, 28, as quoted in B. F. Westcott, <i>A General Survey of
