</div>

<div id=ftn17>

<p class=MsoFootnoteText><a href="#_ftnref17" name="_ftn17" title=""><span
class=MsoFootnoteReference><span class=MsoFootnoteReference><span
style='font-size:13.0pt;font-family:"Garamond","serif"'>[17]</span></span></span></a>
Pfeiffer, <i>History of</i> <i>Classical Scholarship</i>, 207; Jan Gorak, <i>The
